                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6172" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0193</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8259 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“瓜股”疗“商”，助力“双百行动”——冠农股份的 股权激励之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Carving up shares&quot; treat &quot;business&quot; and help &quot;double-hundred reform&quot;-XinJiang Guannong Fruit &amp; Antler Co.,Ltd&#39; equity incentive road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李季鹏，黄永胜</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新疆财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新疆冠农果茸股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">21 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">股权激励；限制性股票；双百企业；考核指标；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Equity incentives; restricted stocks; double-hundred enterprises; assessment indicators</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着我国经济的发展放缓，对国有企业的改革也越来越深化。国有企 业作为我国市场经济的重要组成部分，发展遇到乏力期，面临着升级和改造，与 此同时，核心、专业的优秀人才也从国有企业流失。对有较强代表性、较大发展 潜力、有较强改革意愿的国有企业进行改革，股权激励计划是一项盘活优质资产、 留住优秀人才的可行方案。本案例对入选“双百企业”的新疆冠农果茸股份有限 公司的股权激励进行了详细、全面的阐述，包括实施前因和背景，冠农股份如何 根据自身的情况，选择股票来源、激励对象、激励模式、有效日期、行权价格和 考核指标，从而制定一个适合自己的方案，以及股权激励方案的审议过程和核心 内容。旨在引导学生了解和熟悉股权激励的过程，巩固股权激励方面理论知识。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the slowdown of my country&#39;s economic development, the reform of state-owned enterprises is also deepening. As an important part of my country&#39;s market economy, state-owned enterprises are experiencing a period of weak development and are facing upgrading and transformation. At the same time, core and professional talents are also drained from state-owned enterprises. For the reform of state-owned enterprises with strong representation, greater development potential, and strong willingness to reform, the equity incentive plan is a feasible plan to revitalize high-quality assets and retain excellent talents. This case provides a detailed and comprehensive explanation of the equity incentives of XinJiang Guannong Fruit &amp; Antler Co.,Ltd., which is selected as the &quot;Double Hundred Enterprise&quot;, including the implementation antecedents and background, and how Guannong shares chooses stock sources and incentives according to its own circumstances. Objects, incentive models, effective dates, exercise prices and evaluation indicators, so as to formulate a suitable plan, as well as the review process and core content of the equity incentive plan. It aims to guide students to understand and familiarize themselves with the process of equity incentives and consolidate their theoretical knowledge on equity incentives.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》、《企业战略管理》、《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">对国有企业的股权激励</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
